---
title:  Candidato(a) John Smith
---

<section id="candidate" ng-controller="CandidateController">
  
  <div class="candidate-header container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 text-left">
        <h1 class="nome-candidato">
          <span class="nome">John Smith</span>
          <i class="fa fa-circle"></i>
          <span class="partido">PCdoB</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="assuntos">Assunto 1, Assunto 2, Assunto 3, Assunto 4</p>
        <p class="cidade">São Paulo - SP</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 text-right">
        <img src="/images/mocks/candidate-stamp.png" class="profile-stamp" alt="">
        <img src="/images/mocks/candidate-stamp.png" class="profile-stamp" alt="">
        <img src="/images/mocks/candidate-stamp.png" class="profile-stamp" alt="">
        <img src="/images/mocks/candidate-stamp.png" class="profile-stamp" alt="">
        <img src="/images/mocks/candidate-profile.png" class="profile-image" alt="">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid degrade-default">
    <div class="container" style="margin-top: 80px;">
      <div class="row" style="min-height: 500px; margin-bottom: 30px">
        <div class="candidate-video col-md-7">
          <div class="video-container">
            <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xZKg2w3iOMo" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
          <br class="divider">
          <div class="share-button">
            <ul class="nav nav-pills">
              <li class="disabled"><strong>Compartilhe:</strong></li>
              <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i> Tweet</a></li>
              <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i> Share</a></li>
              <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-youtube"></i> Embed</a></li>
              <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-pinterest"></i> Pin</a></li>
              <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> Post</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <br class="divider">
          <p>Est dolore esse voluptatum est. Vero facilis omnis magni sed sed. Quia illum asperiores pariatur et et rem. Aut ad quas vel esse accusantium recusandae. Id quisquam libero non quia. Modi sit atque possimus assumenda doloremque debitis.</p>
          <p>Et exercitationem sequi maiores sed quidem voluptatibus. Ratione et eligendi consequatur asperiores doloremque sint est. Voluptatem nam adipisci itaque voluptas. Ipsam vel est beatae repudiandae voluptatem rerum. Non quia vitae maiores magni quaerat.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="candidate-campaign col-md-5">
          <h4 class="text-success">Total arrecadado</h4>
          <p class="donated">R$ 90.000</p>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <div class="progress">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="40" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 40%">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-left">
              <small>52%</small>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-right">
              <small>Faltam 10 dias</small>
            </div>
          </div>

          <br class="divider">
          <br class="divider">

          <h4 class="text-success">Pessoas já Doaram</h4>
          <p class="donator-number">125</p>
          <h4 class="text-success">Meta</h4>
          <p class="raising-goal">R$ 100.000</p>

          <p><a class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block btn-donate" href="">Doar</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="candidate-tabs col-md-12">
        
          <!-- Nav tabs -->
          <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
            <li class="active"><a href="#tab-projetos" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Projetos prioritários</a></li>
            <li><a href="#tab-contas" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Prestação de contas</a></li>
            <li><a href="#tab-historico" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Histórico de doações</a></li>
            <li><a href="#tab-sobre" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Sobre mim</a></li>
            <li><a href="#tab-denuncia" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Denunciar</a></li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Tab panes -->
          <div class="tab-content">
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane active" id="tab-projetos">
              <div class="row">
                <% 4.times.each do |i| %>
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <h5>Projeto <%= i + 1 %>) <%= lorem.words 5 %></h5>
                  <p><%= lorem.paragraph %>.</p>
                  <p><%= lorem.paragraph %>.</p>
                </div>
                <% end %>

                <br class="divider">
              </div>

              <hr>

              <div class="project-votes row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <h4 class="text-success">Projetos de lei mais votados:</h4>
                </div>

              <% 4.times.each do |i| %>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <span class="text-muted">Projeto <%= i + 1 %>) <%= lorem.words 5 %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                  <div class="progress">
                    <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success" role="progressbar" style="width: <%= Random.rand(100)%>%">
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-2">
                  <small>51 votos (58%)</small>
                </div>
              <% end %>

              </div>
            </div>
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="tab-contas">
              <br class="divider">
              
              <p>Faça o download da planilha simplificada de gastos da campanha de Joana Rocha:</p>
              <p><a class="btn btn-success btn-lg" href="#"> <i class="fa fa-download"></i> Fazer download da planilha </a></p>
            </div>
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="tab-historico">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <h4>
                    Projetos de lei mais votados:
                    <a class="btn btn-link pull-right" href="#"> <i class="fa fa-download"></i> Imprimir</a>&nbsp;
                    <a class="btn btn-link pull-right" href="#"> <i class="fa fa-print"></i> Download</a>&nbsp;
                  </h4>

                  <br class="divider">
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th>Nome do doador:</th>
                        <th>CEP:</th>
                        <th>Valor doado:</th>
                        <th>Data:</th>
                        <th class="hide">Projetos escolhidos</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      <% 10.times.each do %>
                      <tr>
                        <td><%= lorem.name %></td>
                        <td>99999-99</td>
                        <td>R$ <%= Random.rand(100)%>,00</td>
                        <td>25.12.1990</td>
                        <td class="hide"></td>
                      </tr>
                      <% end %>
                    </tbody>
                  </table>

                  <br class="divider">

                  <p class="text-center">
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="#">Carregar mais</a>
                  </p>
                </div>

              </div>
            </div>
            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="tab-sobre">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <h2 class="nome-candidato">
                    <span class="nome">John Smith</span>
                    <i class="fa fa-circle"></i>
                    <span class="partido">PCdoB</span>
                  </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                  <img src="/images/mocks/user04.jpg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-9">
                  <p><%= lorem.paragraph %></p>
                  <p><%= lorem.paragraph %></p>
                  <p><%= lorem.paragraph %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-12">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="tab-denuncia">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <h5>Caso o candidato apresente alguma irregularidade, preencha o formulário abaixo:</h5>
                  <br>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-offset-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="Seu nome completo">
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="Seu e-mail">
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="Motivo da denúncia">
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <textarea id="" class="form-control" name="" cols="30" rows="10" placeholder="Mensagem"></textarea>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group text-center">
                    <button class="btn btn-success">Enviar</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        
        </div>
      </div>


    </div><!--/container-->
  </div>
</section>
